    example: "Francis famously wrote, 'You can catch more flies with a spoonful of honey than with a hundred barrels of vinegar.' When tasked with reconverting the Chablais region from Calvinism, he slipped pamphlets under doors when people refused to hear him preach — and within four years, the vast majority had returned to Catholicism.",
